description: This header file declares functions for dumping agent info tree and tunneled messages related to the MAP data model in a network system. It includes external references to map_data_model.h and provides API documentation.

methods.name: map_dm_dump_agent_info_tree
methods.description: Function to dump the agent info tree to a terminal using a callback.

methods.name: map_dm_dump_tunneled_messages
methods.description: Function to dump tunneled messages, parameterized by callback, station MAC address, and message type.
